cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.MA 

This paper deals with real-time remote estimation in wireless networked control systems, which involves the integration of control theory, communication theory, and signal processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also proposes a new optimization problem to minimize the long-term remote estimation mean squared error, which involves mathematical analysis and optimization techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a possible category. Finally, the paper deals with linear time-invariant dynamic systems, which falls under cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
